Class EnumMapper<T extends java.lang.Enum<T>,U extends java.lang.Enum<U>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.utils.mapper.impl.MapperObject<T,U>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the enum type of the origin object
    U - the enum type of the destination object

    public class EnumMapper<T extends java.lang.Enum<T>,U extends java.lang.Enum<U>>
extends MapperObject<T,U>
    This class customize the abstract class MapperObject creating a MapperObject that convert on enum type T into a enum U.
    Author:
    eschoysman
    See Also:
    MapperObject, ClassMapper, DirectMapper
